## 12. ⚙️ Functional Requirements

- System should validate policy number  
- System should fetch data from backend API  
- System should respond within 5 seconds  
- System should support retry for failures  

---

## 13. 🚫 Non-Functional Requirements

- Response time < 5 seconds  
- 99.9% uptime  
- Secure data handling (encryption)  
- Scalable to 10,000 concurrent users  

---

